{
  "stem": "1042.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were working, the Czechs, there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the same, you know, around our place, when we were working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when they run away from there, and they left all the merchandise, Schindler, before he left, he took quite a few people to cut for all of us, for three suits, for six shirts, and underwear, and he gave us parcels, you know?",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We shall have with us, because we were poor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were in the-- the-- the-- the suits what we used to wear in the-- in the camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were with the stripes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we came to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We came and the Czechs, you know, they took us very nice of everywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They gave us space to-- to sleep, and for the horses and food for the horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we used to go, you know, three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we come to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Krakow, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I find out nobody is here, my  family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't expect much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was counting maybe some miracle happened, that somebody survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I find those, my two friends, the husband and wife what I took their daughter through, you know, from the ghetto out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were-- they were earlier, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because in Poland, it was three months earlier that-- what they left-- the-- the Jews in, you know, three months earlier.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they were already, and they took me to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I shall live with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had our house what the parents left, but I went with them, and since that time, we were together.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
